{"tid":718660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"資深傳媒人直擊疑犯被捕","createTime":"2018-06-27T00:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T01:58:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4b7e8bf97ba8b0a57b9accd1efccb781b11607","tid":718660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:51:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180627/20432971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20432971&d=%2BJAk%2FLh3C89cP9fo2tcC3b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=48fa8dac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20432971&h=85905504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180627/20432971</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月27日 <br />\n<br />\n資深傳媒人直擊疑犯被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180627/large/a0405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180627%2Flarge%2Fa0405a.gif&h=49260e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭明仁趕抵疑犯被制服現場，商場已圍上圍板。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】鰂魚涌公園開槍案嚇煞街坊，居於太古城的《蘋果日報》前高層鄭明仁，事發後聽聞事件亦趕往了解。他看到商場內圍上圍板，女疑犯在圍板後面已被制服，不禁舒一口氣，他指當時女疑犯身處的不遠處，設有迪士尼遊樂設施，內有不少小孩子在玩耍；一旦女疑犯繼續逃跑，恐造成更多人命傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指案發地點較僻靜<br />\n<br />\n人稱「仁哥」的資深傳媒人鄭明仁，居於太古城多年，昨午事發時他正在商場內咖啡店看書兼嘆咖啡。其間他看即時新聞得知發生開槍案，大批警員正在商場附近搜捕疑兇，他連忙趕往了解。<br />\n<br />\n當他到達現場後，即見大批記者在場，包括《蘋果日報》的舊部，商場內已圍上圍板，所知女疑犯被制服在圍板後面。仁哥在現場直擊指：「當時唔知（女疑犯）仲有冇槍喺身，行過少少就有迪士尼設施，好多細路仔喺度玩，如果佢走甩仲有槍喺身，就好危險嘞！」<br />\n<br />\n仁哥指案發的鰂魚涌公園「耐不耐就有啲嘢發生，打劫都有」，主要是公園比較僻靜，尤其入夜後途人更少，加上公園內有矮樹叢，易生危險。不過他不太擔心今次案件後的安全，形容「太古城嘅治安一向幾好」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎國剛  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n區議員感謝保安專業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑犯經營保鑣公司　搏擊射術皆精<br />\n<br />\n已故外婆留物業作遺產<br />\n<br />\n建3網站對親戚「血的控訴」<br />\n<br />\n鰂魚涌公園嘭嘭聲　街坊嚇到彈起<br />\n<br />\n意製「掌心雷」10米內致命<br />\n<br />\n反恐特勤隊到場戒備<br />\n<br />\n區議員感謝保安專業<br />\n<br />\n女保鑣陀槍爭產擊斃二姨　重創三四舅"},{"pid":"19731039b8e92668024b3b2ef3431f1e2755cd75","tid":718660,"uid":56698,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:53:26.000Z","msg":"廢老飲Starbucks睇熱鬧啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b79556b0d152c821d170934eac2c4d95cc995a3","tid":718660,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:54:18.000Z","msg":"飲完茶去趁熱鬧？"},{"pid":"e0ed64e2114833fb610259ef847f376f8f55faa2","tid":718660,"uid":29093,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"腥港啲傳媒易撈， 去到現場影下圍版就叫直擊"},{"pid":"3b951636416011e0ff4348abf00caa003b22d99d","tid":718660,"uid":95,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"19731039b8e92668024b3b2ef3431f1e2755cd75","tid":718660,"uid":56698,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:53:26.000Z","msg":"廢老飲Starbucks睇熱鬧啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:59:26.000Z","msg":"係，仲講到好似好威咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213139559351a4ad2db00c54bbda35f380ce2e51","tid":718660,"uid":152123,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:02:21.000Z","msg":"內有不少小孩子在玩耍；一旦女疑犯繼續逃跑，恐造成更多人命傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n女疑犯目標明確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 射完就收手"},{"pid":"a85695bc7b3151776005607d13be33f63e237bc6","tid":718660,"uid":13308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:04:38.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影張咁既相就當新聞"},{"pid":"6bbc72ab663a0ac8a05832254483834987f7bb00","tid":718660,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"應該興幸個女人冇打算反抗，如果唔係50發子彈夠死好多人。"},{"pid":"ca7bb8b18faf33cc6730775ba377a0e8106b7a8c","tid":718660,"uid":8921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:12:08.000Z","msg":"個topic係咪有啲語病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8276b66326f7c50cef54e5dd9eb733f161c8d539","tid":718660,"uid":181819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"以為影野影到比人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dd1af6d80c503d63e8dcf7fcf11c3ba0348286","tid":718660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8276b66326f7c50cef54e5dd9eb733f161c8d539","tid":718660,"uid":181819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"以為影野影到比人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:27:45.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e840f69d2ac7043fe8fc5406f83cc6df3d9ef2e9","tid":718660,"uid":38173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"睇 Topic 諗住有咩好似戰地記者咁上下專業直擊報導什至有片睇下<br />\n<br />\n入到黎原來話比我知個廢老舊同事經過見到塊圍版, 連相都無張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031c176a2d00a85ca24ceb652e21eb0620d37f14","tid":718660,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"以為資深傳媒人被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d035272ddc8133c695716751c559a4a3eaa69c","tid":718660,"uid":125479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":